o, binarity seems to play a major role in the isolation of LBVs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2017 22:20:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Sep 2017 21:51:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-28"}
