dded. This result can be explained if to assume the existence of\nsilicon acid shell around the colloidal particles of silver besilicate. The\nmodel of silicon acid shell around colloids was proved by high resolution\nelectron microscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2017 10:52:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-24"}
